{% extends "layouts/default.njk" %}

{% block body %}
<div class="container">
  <h1>This is how people build their side projects</h1>

  <p class="lead">Simple and straightforward NodeJS framework</p>

  <p>
  	<a href="https://github.com/starterkit-io/starterkit" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">
  		<i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> Fork from Github
  	</a>

		<a href="https://heroku.com/deploy?template=https://github.com/starterkit-io/starterkit/">
	  	<img src="https://www.herokucdn.com/deploy/button.svg" alt="Deploy">
		</a>
  </p>
  <br/>
</div>

<hr/>

<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h3>Only the best libraries</h3>
			<p>We only use the best open-source libraries and ones with at least 500 stars.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h3>Batteries included</h3>
			<p>We have included <strong>templating engine</strong>, <strong>user authentication</strong> and <strong>email sending</strong>.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h3>Minimal documentation</h3>
			<p>Straightforward implementation and proper code documentation.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h3>Ready for Cloud</h3>
			<p>It is ready to deploy to <a href="https://heroku.com" target="_blank">Heroku</a>. <em>AWS ElasticBeanstalk coming soon.</em></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h3>Monitoring Services included</h3>
			<p>The system is setup with the best monitoring tools - <a href="https://trace.risingstack.com" target="_blank">Trace</a>, <a href="https://logdna.com" target="_blank">LogDNA</a> and <a href="https://librato.com" target="_blank">Liberato</a>.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h3>Secure System</h3>
			<p>The system will be using <a href="https://github.com/expressjs/csurf" target="_blank">CSRF protection</a> and <a href="https://cloudflare.com/" target="_blank">SSL by CloudFlare</a> to secure the site.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
